  "title": "1 Small Lie: Martin Dockery",
  "description": "A family man robs a thief of a ton of money. Humour, horror, &amp; propulsive music combine in Dockery’s dazzling true-crime story of greed &amp; lies. Like the love child of Breaking Bad &amp; Fargo, this is a suspenseful, edge-of-your-seat thriller! Recent shows: TRUTH, The Stakeout, Inescapable, &amp; Every Good Story Ends With One.",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Martin Dockery<br><strong>Cast</strong>: Martin Dockery<br/><strong>Designers</strong>: Martin Dockery<br/></br>",
  "website": "https://martindockery.com",
  "plain_language": "A family man steals a big bag of money from a thief and is caught in an ever-expanding web of lies. Like Breaking Bad, Fargo, and A Simple Plan, this is a knuckle-biting thriller about the corrupting power of greed. The show’s got a pretty cool soundtrack, too.",
